      "review_summary": "The PR adds an owner-or-Gateway-operator.admin guard before /plugins install, enable, or disable can mutate plugin state, with regression tests for non-owner channel attempts and Gateway admin allow paths.\n\nPR surface: Source +11, Tests +118. Total +129 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current main lets channel-authorized native /plugins writes with absent Gateway scopes reach mutation handling without an owner check, and the docs define plugin writes as owner-only.",
